<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>New Player!</h1>
    <p><a href="http://nowplay.us/users/<%= @view.player.slug %>"><%= @view.player %></a> is in for the game of <a href="http://nowplay.us/events/<%= @view.event.id %>"><%= @view.title %></a> on <%= @view.scheduled_time_with_date %></p>
    <hr>
    <p>
      <small>
        This email was sent to <%= @view.to_email %> from Now Play Us because you elected to receive notifications for comments on events in which you participate. If you wish, you can <a href="http://nowplay.us/unwatch/<%= @view.notification_subscription.to_param %>">turn off notifications for <%= @view.title %> on <%= @view.scheduled_time_with_date %></a>.
      </small>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>